Sample Microsoft Cobol Ver 2.x program notes.

In order to call Opt-Tech Sort directly from MS 
Cobol Ver 2.x you must link Opt-Tech Sort into your 
RUNCOB.EXE file.  A summary of how to accomplish 
this is given below.  

1. Edit USERPROG.MAC and add the line SORTIC,ASM86
2. Assemble the program ASM.ASM
3. LINK COBOL ASM,RUNCOB,,COBOL1 COBOL2 SORT /NOD
4. INSTALL RUNCOB.EXE

More information is provided in your Cobol manual 
under "Calling Non-Cobol Subroutines".
